{"tid":1299836,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"多功能智慧燈柱資料整合","createTime":"2019-07-09T07:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:49:09.000Z","uid":106480,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c3df54199398200db58bf2215ce84f485f3a200a","tid":1299836,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"現略為整合網上可獲取之智能燈柱資料，希望各位巴打對事情有更深既了解。<br />\n<br />\n所有資料都係政府網站與各大新聞網整合，全部係政府自己放出來<br />\n<br />\n本身政府於2017年提出「香港智慧城市藍圖」，其附屬「多功能智慧燈柱」試驗計畫係四個市區地點（中環／金鐘、銅鑼灣／灣仔、尖沙咀及觀塘／啟德發展區），安裝約 400 支附設智能裝置的多功能智慧燈柱，協助相關部門收集各類實時城市數據，加強城市和交通管理。 <br />\n<br />\n咁個燈柱咩樣呢? 就係好似一棵草咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/05/20190509/20190509_120413_056/images/20190509121408885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F05%2F20190509%2F20190509_120413_056%2Fimages%2F20190509121408885.jpg&h=5d7b252a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面就有360度既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交通探測器</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全景攝影機</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2345000/2349917/20190509121525023_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2345000%2F2349917%2F20190509121525023_1024_600.jpg&h=a835e788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面就裝左:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WiFi，4G，5G</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">藍牙</span></strong>(Bluetooth)<br />\n無線射頻識別（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">RFID</span></strong>）(<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以detect新型身分證</span></strong>)<br />\n地理二維碼(QR code)<br />\n<br />\n枝燈柱將會收集:<br />\n交通數據 (車輛速度、車輛類型、交通流量/監察交通情況等) <br />\n空氣質素<br />\n氣象相關數據(氣溫、濕度、風速和風向、降雨量、紫外線指數等)<br />\n<br />\n之前就已經講過2019年6月底就會啟用觀塘&amp;啟德發展區既50枝監控燈柱，暫時有7枝係有詳細位置。<br />\n<br />\n起動九龍東辦事處<br />\n反轉天橋底一號場<br />\n反轉天橋底三號場<br />\n機電工程署總部<br />\n啟德郵輪碼頭<br />\n零碳天地<br />\n啟德跑道公園碼頭<br />\n來源:<a href=\"https://data.gov.hk/tc-data/dataset/hk-devb-mplp-mplp-sensor-data\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.gov.hk%2Ftc-data%2Fdataset%2Fhk-devb-mplp-mplp-sensor-data&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=6903f823\" target=\"_blank\">https://data.gov.hk/tc-data/dataset/hk-devb-mplp-mplp-sensor-data</a><br />\n<br />\n政府都有列出呢7枝燈柱主要收集到咩數據<br />\n<a href=\"https://mplpssl.wisx.io/docs/Data_Specification_for_mplp-sensor-data_PSI_TC.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmplpssl.wisx.io%2Fdocs%2FData_Specification_for_mplp-sensor-data_PSI_TC.pdf&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=9d5d7c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://mplpssl.wisx.io/docs/Data_Specification_for_mplp-sensor-data_PSI_TC.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n其餘50枝既位置就未搵到有地圖公開，但新聞曾經列出過:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">康寧道、大業街、駿業街、勵業街及 觀塘道/開源道</span></strong><br />\n中環和金鐘、銅鑼灣和灣仔的智慧燈柱就預計今年年底啟用。<br />\n<br />\n根據「香港智慧城市藍圖」說法，政府係打算係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年建立新的大數據分析平台</span></strong>，讓政府部門能互相實時傳送同分享數據。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而所有資料都會upload上新既政府雲端平台，比政府部門同其他第三方的協作&amp;合作去提供服務。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">除此之外九龍東仲開發左一套流動安裝既監察系統<br />\n以應付各種情況既活動需要去監控同獲取即時數據。<br />\n<br />\n由安裝到可以使用係需時少於30分鐘<br />\n所以冇監控燈柱情況下政府都可以用呢種方法去獲取資料</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P5n8oJgbico&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP5n8oJgbico%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=39d2d900\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P5n8oJgbico&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"5f315b3a0e21fd1252e84b4767c40cbf1eaea4f4","tid":1299836,"uid":6674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ih0.redbubble.net/image.624393553.1886/flat,550x550,075,f.u5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fih0.redbubble.net%2Fimage.624393553.1886%2Fflat%2C550x550%2C075%2Cf.u5.jpg&h=17fc3d06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46309947eba3ac1df8e550f62bd1f2eed0567091","tid":1299836,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>補充資料</strong><br />\n<br />\n政府自製既九龍東既智慧城市地圖資料:<br />\n<a href=\"http://mapping.arup.com/smartke/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmapping.arup.com%2Fsmartke%2Fen&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=8b9863df\" target=\"_blank\">http://mapping.arup.com/smartke/en</a><br />\n<br />\n星島日報既燈柱報導:<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1938433-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E8%A3%9D44%E6%94%AF%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1+%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%8C%E6%94%BE%E5%85%89%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1938433-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E8%25A3%259D44%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1%2B%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2585%2589%25E3%2580%258D&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=2f254969\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1938433-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E8%25A3%259D44%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1%2B%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2585%2589%25E3%2580%258D&h=84621d91\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1938433-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E8%A3%9D44%E6%94%AF%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1+%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%8C%E6%94%BE%E5%85%89%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n資訊科技及廣播事務委員會 2019年4月16日舉行的會議<br />\n有關發展智慧城市的最新背景資料簡介(共13頁):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/itb/papers/itb20190416cb1-876-4-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fitb%2Fpapers%2Fitb20190416cb1-876-4-c.pdf&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=fde2c5d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/itb/papers/itb20190416cb1-876-4-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會<br />\n發展智慧城市的最新情況 - 立法會CB(1)876/18-19(03)號文件(共9頁)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ogcio.gov.hk/tc/news/legco_papers/2019/04/doc/lb_20190416.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ogcio.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Flegco_papers%2F2019%2F04%2Fdoc%2Flb_20190416.pdf&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=c78ee984\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ogcio.gov.hk/tc/news/legco_papers/2019/04/doc/lb_20190416.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n香港科學園智能燈柱收集的數據:<br />\n<a href=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201804/25/P2018042500333_282370_1_1524627857026.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201804%2F25%2FP2018042500333_282370_1_1524627857026.pdf&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1YoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=44dc04a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201804/25/P2018042500333_282370_1_1524627857026.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"8496bd62b732bcc4bc8601778fc6cb07d90e3922","tid":1299836,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"試著說監控燈柱"},{"pid":"028ece13a5b4f2b55a2b9194ece0d9581ef27ae6","tid":1299836,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"監控燈柱！"},{"pid":"9c209b38c80b10e749491cb6f07b65ce0c9d174f","tid":1299836,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"25b67a97cd3de57bde18fcd6ef844b2f01052205","tid":1299836,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-